location.fullValue: Bristol Plan, Homes of Liberty Place

data.description: RANCH with 3 CAR GARAGE and MAIN FLOOR LAUNDRY. Check out this well maintained home in Liberty Place. This home feature a formal foyer leading into an open concept home. Vaulted ceilings throughout the primary living areas add a degree of architectural detail. Kitchen has wood cabinets with crown, recessed lighting, pantry and breakfast bar. Kitchen leads to laundry just off 3 car garage. Dining is open to kitchen and living and features bay style sliding glass doors out to fully fenced yard. Living room and foyer are updated with Hickory finish vinyl plank. Gas fireplace flanked by windows highlight the vaulted ceiling with plant shelf. Mater bedroom has tray ceiling, walk in closet, master bath  2022 remodel with new flooring, walk in shower and existing jetted tub.  2 more nice size bedrooms and hall bath complete the main. Lower level has painted flooring, large family area, separate office/bonus/craft room and lots of storage.  Seller to put on NEW ROOF WITH RIGHT OFFER!
